atrade is an experimental automated algorithmic trading platform
atrade is a work in progress and not guaranteed in any way

Source Files
------------
main.py - main file that is called to start trading platform

common.py - defines global variables and imports common modules
  
scanner.py - handles asynchronous market scan and data regression

handlers.py - holds algos that determine act upon current market state

ibx.py - connects to an Interactive Brokers account and trades using ib_insync API

classes.py - holds utility classes

setup.py - install the atrade platform and binds the atrade command to your shell


Installation
------------
1: Download and extract or clone this repository
2: Navigate to the installation directory from the command line
3: Enter the following command: pip3 install .

